 Stock were represented in person or by proxy and, therefore, a quorum was present.Proposal 1.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2304, "end_char_idx": 2677, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "62695575-f1d1-4031-9b7f-d7da2ede824a": {"__data__": {"id_": "62695575-f1d1-4031-9b7f-d7da2ede824a", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "d8f60210-71af-49ec-bae3-612df9fa1940", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "c1c17f6a2fe93379310cdad464ba03049a7f5aaee467e7ccc558efaad66d8e4f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "7ee7eceb-e92e-4673-8a70-2d8b2ecc5b41", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "5901b6958695106f882847a550247a92c8a4b0bc642d07068d9939fa2117c5dc", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "7a1cc00c-ad73-4419-b87a-51237aa6b3c6", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "b5308b2a6a1f324ee67937b94ed5a17020e632e473eba4ff0590557e87c55615", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "With respect to the proposal to elect ten nominees to the Board of Directors (the \u201cBoard\u201d), each for a one-year term expiring at the annual meeting of shareholders to be held in 2023, the votes were cast for the proposal as set forth below:\nName Votes For Votes Against Abstentions Broker Non-Votes Virginia C. Drosos 59,657,810 294,935 10,714,238 6,884,223 Alan D.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2680, "end_char_idx": 3045, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "7a1cc00c-ad73-4419-b87a-51237aa6b3c6": {"__data__": {"id_": "7a1cc00c-ad73-4419-b87a-51237aa6b3c6", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"nod