atedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "With respect to the proposal, on an advisory basis, whether the shareholder vote to approve the NEOs\u2019 compensation should occur every 1, 2, or 3 years, the votes were cast for the proposal as set forth below:\nVotes For 1 Year Votes For 2 Years Votes For 3 Years Abstentions Broker Non-Votes 66,076,265 43,060 4,352,683 194,975 6,884,223", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 4039, "end_char_idx": 4375, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "4ed0964d-7bce-4e8b-bd5b-eeec78554017": {"__data__": {"id_": "4ed0964d-7bce-4e8b-bd5b-eeec78554017", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "d8f60210-71af-49ec-bae3-612df9fa1940", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "c1c17f6a2fe93379310cdad464ba03049a7f5aaee467e7ccc558efaad66d8e4f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "141ea38a-be3a-40b1-b1ed-04f3877f448a", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "d4951688aae453c72b5005482c961ee240c95e406894477bc9dd2ee28bb93c36", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "7d1376a4-52f5-4041-b736-0c1c9148a618", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "4e70db33fa8db0f8d954c7908a73a766d53288eb79d42079da89207b11cadac2", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Based  on  the  votes  set  forth  above,  the  Company  will  include  an  annual  advisory  shareholder  vote  to  approve  the  NEOs\u2019  compensation  in  its proxy materials until the next required frequency vote, which is expected to be held at the annual meeting of shareholders to be held in 2028.Proposal 4.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 4378, "end_char_idx": 4691, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "7d1376a4-52f5-4041-b736-0c1c9148a618": {"__data__": {"id_": "7d1376a4-52f5-4041-b736-0c1c9148a618", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "d8f60210-71af-49ec-bae3-612df9fa1940", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "c1c17f6a2fe93379310cdad464ba03049a7f5aaee467e7ccc558efaad66d8e4f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "4ed0964d-7bce-4e8b-bd5b-eeec78554017", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "5600129467d5d8e5319a6403bf6b5de43d2d58434ccfe459f6a57ce9ca7364a7", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "c54f2c4c-c634-460b-a71f-5013e16a4c65", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "f070f1b20faf4c40d086441d3c15237a10243adbb0cf19f1fe98702f44bb324e", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "With respect to the proposal to ratify the appointment of KPMG LLP as the Company\u2019s independent registered public accounting firm for the 2022 fiscal year, the votes were cast for the proposal as set forth below:\nVotes For Votes Against Abstentions 75,612,318 1,854,695 84,193", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 4694, "end_char_idx": 4970, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "c54f2c4c-c634-460b-a71f-5013e16a4c65": {"__data__": {"id_": "c54f2c4c-c634-460b-a71f-5013e16a4c65", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "d8f60210-71af-49ec-bae3-612df9fa1940", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "c1c17f6a2fe93379310cdad464ba03049a7f5aaee467e7ccc558efaad66d8e4f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "7d1376a4-52f5-4041-b736-0c1c9148a618", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "4e70db33fa8db0f8d954c7908a73a766d53288eb79d42079da89207b11cadac2", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "562ef993-52a2-48ca-8dab-823cb6290e72", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a07371153c001a98b859bdd0987b7a4fee8c5beaae87cccbdc3f4013df2971c6", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Based on the votes set forth above, the appointment of KPMG LLP as the Company\u2019s independent registered public accounting firm for the 2022 fiscal year was duly ratified.\n\nItem 8.01. Other Events.\n\nOn May 18, 2022, in light of Matthew McKenna\u2019s retirement, the Board designated Ms. Nicosia as the \u201caudit committee financial expert.\u201d In connection with this designation, the Board determined that Ms.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 4973, "end_char_idx": 5372, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "562ef993-52a2-48ca-8dab-823cb6290e72": {"__data__": {"id_": "562ef993-52a2-48ca-8dab-823cb6290e72", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "d8f60210-71af-49ec-bae3-612df9fa1940", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "c1c17f6a2fe93379310cdad464ba03049a7f5aaee467e7ccc558efaad66d8e4f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "c54f2c4c-c634-460b-a71f-5013e16a4c65", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "f070f1b20faf4c40d086441d3c15237a10243adbb0cf19f1fe98702f44bb324e", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "48abbc40-6712-470a-8491-efdb97311964", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "183446903b91e9fda13345dfc5d1eea8bad31c681adf5aeeb99672777641d054", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Nicosia qualifies as an \u201caudit committee financial expert,\u201d as defined by the rules under the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, as amended (the \u201cExchange Act\u201d), because of her relevant experience as president of an operating unit of a large multinational corporation.\n\n She has supervised the finance and accounting professionals responsible for, and personally analyzed and evaluated, financial statements, as well as internal controls over financial reporting.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 5373, "end_char_idx": 5834, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "48abbc40-6712-470a-8491-efdb97311964": {"__data__": {"id_": "48abbc40-6712-470a-8491-efdb97311964", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "d8f60210-71af-49ec-bae3-612df9fa1940", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "c1c17f6a2fe93379310cdad464ba03049a7f5aaee467e7ccc558efaad66d8e4f", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "562ef993-52a2-48ca-8dab-823cb6290e72", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a07371153c001a98b859bdd0987b7a4fee8c5beaae87cccbdc3f4013df2971c6", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "1e12a1ad-f3f7-42de-9961-a9be398587bc", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "abdc394cff07252f39ead594bc045a773b43e10f84cca2b5dc001b06b2836e27", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "She is also familiar with audit committee functions through her service on the Company\u2019s Audit Committee. The Board also believes that there are other directors who would also qualify for this designation.Item 9.01. Financial Statements and Exhibits.(d)\nExhibits. Exhibit No.\n\nDescription\n\n104\nCover Page Interactive Data File (embedded within the Inline XBRL document).", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 5835, "end_char_idx": 6205, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, 